name: OCKAnyReadOnlyContactStore
desc: A read-only custom store that fetches contact data objects.

items.name: var contactDelegate: OCKContactStoreDelegate?
items.desc: The object that handles callbacks from a contact store when the contents of the contact store change.

items.name: func fetchAnyContact(withID: String, callbackQueue: DispatchQueue, completion: OCKResultClosure<OCKAnyContact>)
items.desc: Fetches a contact asynchronously from the store.

items.name: func fetchAnyContacts(query: OCKAnyContactQuery, callbackQueue: DispatchQueue, completion: OCKResultClosure<[OCKAnyContact]>)
items.desc: Fetches an array of contact asynchronously from the store.
